query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS progress_predictions (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  studentId INT NOT NULL,
  goalId INT,
  predictionType VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  predictedValue VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  confidence INT,
  factors JSON,
  recommendations JSON,
  generatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX student_idx (studentId),
  INDEX goal_idx (goalId)
);
